                              Employer Services

      Employer Services on USAJOBS enables organizations to add job
      information to the USAJOBS database. Information added through the Job
      Entry Program will appear on the web site and through USAJOBS by Phone.

      If you are seeking a job or need other employment information, please
      return to the home page to access Job Openings and our other services.

      If you work in a human resource or administrative office and want to
      announce jobs on the site, you must have pre-approved access. Please
      select here to register to use the Job Entry Program.


